snippet.textDisplay:
My Fellow Indians, as you now know Tu chiz badi hai mast mast is actually copied from Nusrat Sahab's Dam Mast Qalandar.... also note that 'Mera Piya Ghar aaya O Ramji' is copied from 'Mera Piya Ghar aaya O Lalani' a Kalma by Baba Bulleh Shah adopted as Qawali by Nusrat Sahab :)

Undoubtedly the tribute is Amazing and really well done! Love from India :)
